{"tid":1836522,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一名澳洲旅客進入麥理浩夫人度假村隔離","createTime":"2020-01-23T08:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T12:02:35.000Z","uid":212626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"58b12e32cb24a800cfe16272ced6a49f723ba70d","tid":1836522,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T08:38:59.000Z","msg":"衞生防護中心表示，已接觸3名與兩個高度懷疑個案有關的密切接觸者，今日安排麥理浩夫人度假村接受隔離。本台下午在度假村所見，一名澳洲旅客下午乘坐政府專用的白色小巴進入度假村接受隔離，車上有身穿保護衣人員。<br />\n<br />\n該名旅客表示，原本入住沙田帝逸酒店，不清楚需要接受隔離原因，目前感覺良好。<br />\n<br />\n本港現時有兩宗高度懷疑感染新型冠狀病毒個案，第2名患者本月19日由武漢乘坐飛機往深圳，同日經羅湖口岸乘坐港鐵回港，18日起開始發燒，但無呼吸道感染徵狀，翌日到威爾斯醫院急症室求醫，毋須入院。他星期一入住沙田帝逸酒店，第 2日再到同一急症室覆診，由於發燒徵狀持續，院方安排他接受隔離治療，現時情況穩定。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504437-20200123.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504437-20200123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2FpywbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=44631554\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504437-20200123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=45df9964\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504437-20200123.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a7876e177e5410838a6cdfa973e7cc8ec1d3f9aa","tid":1836522,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T08:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />."},{"pid":"6443006cc19dc5568751db540720095cca923999","tid":1836522,"uid":53062,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T08:40:26.000Z","msg":"武漢大陸狗又唔需要隔離<br />\n特府 Good job"},{"pid":"b99c1eb5fe5c361e588a0b6bb55ae1454f5ba9cf","tid":1836522,"uid":219010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"58b12e32cb24a800cfe16272ced6a49f723ba70d","tid":1836522,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T08:38:59.000Z","msg":"衞生防護中心表示，已接觸3名與兩個高度懷疑個案有關的密